What ModShop Does

For Modders (Sellers)

1. One‑click store setup — upload mod, set price, get a branded storefront URL
2. Automatic delivery — customers get download links instantly after purchase
3. Version management — push updates, notify all buyers
4. Analytics dashboard — see sales, traffic, conversion rates
5. No coding required — everything through web interface

For Buyers (Gamers)

1. Instant purchase — pay with card, bank transfer, USSD, or mobile money (via Paystack)
2. Automatic updates — get notified when mods update
3. Library management — all purchased mods in one place
4. Reviews and ratings — quality signals

Technical Architecture (Simple MVP)

```
Frontend: Next.js/React
Backend: Node.js + Express
Database: PostgreSQL
Payments: Paystack (split payments – automatically sends your 10% commission and creator's 87% to separate bank accounts)
File storage: AWS S3 or Cloudflare R2
Delivery: Signed URLs for security
```

Estimated build time: 4‑6 weeks for MVP

